info.headline: Wind Advisory issued December 22 at 10:35PM EST until December 23 at 7:00PM EST by NWS Philadelphia - Mount Holly
info.description: ...WIND ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 7 PM EST FRIDAY... * WHAT...Southwest winds 20 to 30 mph with gusts up to 50 mph. * WHERE...In Delaware, Delaware Beaches. In New Jersey, Western Monmouth, Eastern Monmouth, Ocean, Atlantic, Cape May, Atlantic Coastal Cape May, Coastal Atlantic, Coastal Ocean and Southeastern Burlington. * WHEN...Until 7 PM EST Friday. * IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects. Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may result.
info.instruction: Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.
